summary: A small exterior shack located in the Rift near Faldar\'s Tooth and Heartwood Mill.
descriptionHtml:
A simple shack for ranger or hunter style characters located in the Rift. Includes bed, two chests, a tanning rack, anvil, grindstone, work bench and alchemy/enchanting facilities. A fire with a cooking pot sits just outside.

A few targets are scattered up the hillside for archery practice.

Type \"coc frkHuntersShack\" in the console to teleport there.
author: Freki
